08:03.065 --> 08:06.484
♪ <i> Sailing takes me away...</i> ♪

08:06.485 --> 08:09.112
- What were we fighting about?
- I don't know.

08:09.113 --> 08:12.073
My cares have all
suddenly melted away.

08:12.074 --> 08:15.327
Are my toes tapping?
I feel like my toes are tapping.

08:15.328 --> 08:17.537
Nah, there's a seagull
pecking at your foot.

08:17.538 --> 08:18.872
(squawking)

08:18.873 --> 08:20.540
