- (sighs)

11:15.549 --> 11:18.218
Then I guess
this black shirt is out.

11:18.219 --> 11:20.595
You just want to hang out
with Doug Federman.

11:20.596 --> 11:23.264
What? That's...
that's the wine talking.

11:23.265 --> 11:25.308
